Shotgun is open-source and we welcome contributions. Whether you're fixing bugs, proposing features, improving docs, or spreading the wordâ€”we'd love to have you as part of the community.

### Ways to contribute:

- **Bug Report:** Found an issue? [Create a bug report](https://github.com/shotgun-sh/shotgun/issues/new?template=bug_report.md)
